    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but making a difference in my \"corner\" doesnt change the fact that it's all pointless. it feels like rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. i look at the future and i just see nothing. no stability, no safety, just a slow collapse. how can anyone actually find hope in that? it feels more rational to just not be part of it than to keep pretending things will get better.",
